            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2.25 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e2_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s1_e2",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 0.75,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) تحقق أنه من أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $v_n=3u_{2n}$. ب) استنتج $T_n=u_0+u_2+u_4+\\cdots+u_{2n}$."
