            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "بما أن $u_{2n}=2^{2n}=4^n$ فإن $v_n=3u_{2n}$. ومنه $T_n=\\frac{1}{3}S_n=\\frac{4^{n+1}-1}{3}$."
